I LOVE THAT MAN SOOO FREAKIN MUCH!! You guys did such an amazing job interviewing him🙌🏾 I swooned every time I heard him laugh lol. Please let us know when the TAK podcast has found a new home so I can tune in. I hope Chris can come back one day soon for another amazing interview filled with good laughs.

Girl power!!!

It was long speculated that Captain Marvel would play a major factor in the upcoming Avengers flick.
